    {
      "id": "ann_dp_detail",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 857,
      "y": 860,
      "width": 198.046875,
      "height": 243.75,
      "text": "Triggers ETL pipeline by:\n1. Write raw file to MinIO\n2. MinIO S3 event → Kafka\n\nPipeline consumers:\n  • raw (+ DLQ)\n  • validated (+ DLQ)\n  • mapped (+ DLQ)\n  • processed (+ DLQ)\n\nEach stage: \n  • read data\n  • extract plugin\n  • proceess data\n  • write back to MinIO.",
      "originalText": "Triggers ETL pipeline by:\n1. Write raw file to MinIO\n2. MinIO S3 event → Kafka\n\nPipeline consumers:\n  • raw (+ DLQ)\n  • validated (+ DLQ)\n  • mapped (+ DLQ)\n  • processed (+ DLQ)\n\nEach stage: \n  • read data\n  • extract plugin\n  • proceess data\n  • write back to MinIO.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#047857",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
